{
  "texts": [
    "This second component uses character embeddings and current episode trajectory to formulate a mental state embedding.",
    "The prediction net utilises these mental state embeddings to predict future agent behaviour while the embeddings constantly update.",
    "Rabinowitz et al. (2018) hope this approach will approximate how humans mentalise ToM.",
    "But what about the abductive reasoning capabilities of these systems?",
    "An important thing to consider is that the field of medical imaging -particularly radiology -saw the most widespread use and adoption of AI systems in medicine (Pesapane et al., 2018)."
  ]
}